64 struct nodestruct scan(cv::Mat mazescan, struct nodestruct node){
65 
66  node.dir[4] = mazescan.at<double>(node.y-2,node.x);
67  node.dir[1] = mazescan.at<double>(node.y,node.x+2);
68  node.dir[2] = mazescan.at<double>(node.y+2,node.x);
69  node.dir[3] = mazescan.at<double>(node.y,node.x-2);
70 
71  return node;
72 }

75 int checkForExit(struct nodestruct env){
76 
77  for(int i = 1; i < 5; i++){
78  if(!(env.dir[i] == closed || env.dir[i] == current || env.dir[i] == visited || env.dir[i] == 0 || env.dir[i] == 1))
79  return 1;
80  }
81  return 0;
82 }

120 vector<nodestruct> setStatus(vector<nodestruct> node, double newStatus){
121 
122  int motion = 0;
123 
124  if(newStatus == closed)
125  motion = node[node.size()-1].move;
126  else if(newStatus == visited)
127  motion = node[node.size()-2].move;
128  else
129  cout << "- ERROR -" << endl;
130 
131  switch(motion){
132  case 0:
133  break;
134  case 1:
135  if(newStatus == closed)
136  node[node.size()-1].dir[1] = newStatus;
137  else
138  node[node.size()-1].dir[3] = newStatus;
139  break;
140  case 2:
141  if(newStatus == closed)
142  node[node.size()-1].dir[2] = newStatus;
143  else
144  node[node.size()-1].dir[4] = newStatus;
145  break;
146  case 3:
147  if(newStatus == closed)
148  node[node.size()-1].dir[3] = newStatus;
149  else
150  node[node.size()-1].dir[1] = newStatus;
151  break;
152  case 4:
153  if(newStatus == closed)
154  node[node.size()-1].dir[4] = newStatus;
155  else
156  node[node.size()-1].dir[2] = newStatus;
157  break;
158  }
159 
160  return node;
161 }

177 bool checkIfVisited(vector<nodestruct> &NV){
178  visumaze.at<double>(NV[NV.size()-2].y,NV[NV.size()-2].x) = visited;
179 
180  for(int i = 0; i < (NV.size()-1); i++){
181  if(NV[i].x == NV[NV.size()-1].x && NV[i].y == NV[NV.size()-1].y){
182  cout << " - VISITED BEFORE -" << endl;
183  visumaze.at<double>(NV[NV.size()-1].y,NV[NV.size()-1].x) = 0.1;
184  NV.pop_back();
185  //nodelist.pop_back();
186  NV = setStatus(NV, closed);
187  return 1;
188  }
189  }
190  return 0;
191 }
